01:26:58.195 --> 01:27:00.247
Dok te ne upozna.

01:27:01.725 --> 01:27:05.646
Ponekad sam kreten.
-Ponekad?

01:27:08.875 --> 01:27:11.167
Imaš pravo.

01:27:36.973 --> 01:27:39.046
Japanci znaju da se prikradu.

01:27:40.146 --> 01:27:43.346
